The grant mayv be seen in the same repository as the former, and a reference will be found to it in the same index, (lst and Qud Philip and Mary, rot. 143.) But Hol- crofte’s possession was not yet quieted, for in the 5th Eliza- beth, (ibid, rot. 85,) he was summoned to shew by what title he held the priory. Doubtless he was able to satisfy this summons, although the result does not appear in the index.
